ToolScript


Syntax


<QualifiedName>
    ::= <QualifiedName> '.' ID
    | ID

<Stm>
    ::= if '(' <Expr> ')' <Stm>
    | if '(' <Expr> ')' <Then Stm> else <Stm>
    | while '(' <Expr> ')' <Stm>
    | for '(' <Expr> ';' <Expr> ';' <Expr> ')' <Stm>
    | foreach '(' ID in <Expr> ')' <Stm>
    | using <QualifiedName> ';'
    | using StringLiteral ';'
    | using <QualifiedName> as ID ';'
    | using StringLiteral as ID ';'
    | using '(' <Expr> ')' <Stm>
    | observed '(' <Expr List> ')' <Stm>
    | <Normal Stm>

<Then Stm>
    ::= if '(' <Expr> ')' <Then Stm> else <Then Stm>
    | while '(' <Expr> ')' <Then Stm>
    | for '(' <Expr> ';' <Expr> ';' <Expr> ')' <Then Stm>
    | <Normal Stm>

<Normal Stm>
    ::= do <Stm> while '(' <Expr> ')'
    | switch '(' <Expr> ')' '{' <Case Stms> '}'
    | <Block>
    | <Expr> ';'
    | break ';'
    | continue ';'
    | return <Expr> ';'
    | ';'

<Func args>
    ::= <Func args> ',' <Func Arg>
    | <Func Arg>
    |  

<Func Arg>
    ::= ID
    | ID '=' <Expr>

<Args>
    ::= <Args> ',' <Arg>
    | <Arg>
    |  

<Arg>
    ::= <Op If>
    | ID '=' <Expr>

<Case Stms>
    ::= case <Value> ':' <Stm List> <Case Stms>
    | default ':' <Stm List>
    |  

<Block>
    ::= '{' <Stm List> '}'

<Stm List>
    ::= <Stm> <Stm List>
    | <Stm>

<ID List>
    ::= <ID List> ',' ID
    | ID
    |  

<Database>
    ::= database ID '{' <DB Tables> '}'
    | extends database ID '{' <DB Tables> '}'

<DB Tables>
    ::= <DB Tables> <DB Table>
    |  

<DB Table>
    ::= template table ID '{' <DB Columns> '}' <DB Table Attr List>
    | template table ID template ID '{' <DB Columns> '}' <DB Table Attr List>
    | table ID '{' <DB Columns> '}' <DB Table Attr List>
    | table ID template ID '{' <DB Columns> '}' <DB Table Attr List>
    | extends table ID '{' <DB Columns> '}' <DB Table Attr List>

<DB Columns>
    ::= <DB Columns> <DB Column>
    |  

<DB Column>
    ::= ID <DB Column Type> <DB Column Attr List> ';'

<DB Column Type>
    ::= primary
    | foreign ID
    | foreign ID '(' ID ')'
    | many ID
    | many ID through ID
    | many ID through ID '(' ID ',' ID ')'
    | varchar
    | varchar '(' IntLiteral ')'
    | integer
    | bool
    | decimal '(' IntLiteral ',' IntLiteral ')'
    | date
    | time
    | datetime
    | daterange
    | timerange
    | datetimerange

<DB Column Attr List>
    ::= <DB Column Attr List> <DB Column Attr>
    |  

<DB Column Attr>
    ::= unique
    | not null
    | index
    | default <Value>
    | ID '=' <Value>

<DB Table Attr List>
    ::= <DB Table Attr List> <DB Table Attr>
    |  

<DB Table Attr>
    ::= index '(' <ID List> ')' ';'
    | <DB Trigger Runs> position DecimalLiteral <Stm>
    | ID '=' <Value> ';'

<DB Trigger Runs>
    ::= <DB Trigger Runs> ',' <DB Trigger Run>
    | <DB Trigger Run>

<DB Trigger Run>
    ::= before select
    | after select
    | before insert
    | after insert
    | before update
    | after update
    | before delete
    | after delete
    | before modified
    | after modified

<Function>
    ::= function ID '(' <Func args> ')' <Stm>
    | function '(' <Func args> ')' <Stm>

<Widget>
    ::= window ID <WndParam List> <Layout Block>
    | window <WndParam List> <Layout Block>
    | widget ID <Layout Block>
    | widget <Layout Block>

<WndParam List>
    ::= <WndParam> <WndParam List>
    |  

<WndParam>
    ::= ID '=' <Expr> ';'
    | ID ';'

<Layout List>
    ::= <Layout List> <Layout Block>
    |  

<Layout Block>
    ::= hbox <WndParam List> <Layout List> end
    | vbox <WndParam List> <Layout List> end
    | hbuttonbox <WndParam List> <Layout List> end
    | vbuttonbox <WndParam List> <Layout List> end
    | table <WndParam List> <Layout List> end
    | toolbar <WndParam List> <Layout List> end
    | button <WndParam List> <Layout Block>
    | button <WndParam List> end
    | toolbutton <WndParam List> <Layout Block>
    | toolbutton <WndParam List> end
    | image <WndParam List>
    | StringLiteral <WndParam List>
    | <Menu Block>
    | '[' <Expr> ']' <WndParam List>

<Menu Block>
    ::= menu <WndParam List> <MenuItems List> end

<MenuItems List>
    ::= <Menu Item> <MenuItems List>
    |  

<Menu Item>
    ::= <Menu Block>
    | menuitem <WndParam List>
    | Separator

<Expr List>
    ::= <Expr List> ',' <Expr>
    | <Expr>

<Dict List>
    ::= <Expr> ':' <Expr> ',' <Dict List>
    | <Expr> ':' <Expr>
    |  

<Expr>
    ::= <Widget>
    | <Database>
    | <Op Assign>

<Op Assign>
    ::= <Op If> '=' <Expr>
    | <Op If> '+=' <Expr>
    | <Op If> '-=' <Expr>
    | <Op If> '*=' <Expr>
    | <Op If> '/=' <Expr>
    | <Op If> '<==' <Expr>
    | <Op If> '<==>' <Expr>
    | <Op If>

<Op If>
    ::= <Op Or> '?' <Op If> ':' <Op If>
    | <Op Or>

<Op Or>
    ::= <Op Or> or <Op And>
    | <Op And>

<Op And>
    ::= <Op And> and <Op Equate>
    | <Op Equate>

<Op Equate>
    ::= <Op Equate> '==' <Op Compare>
    | <Op Equate> '!=' <Op Compare>
    | <Op Equate> in <Op Compare>
    | <Op Compare>

<Op Compare>
    ::= <Op Compare> '<' <Op Add>
    | <Op Compare> '>' <Op Add>
    | <Op Compare> '<=' <Op Add>
    | <Op Compare> '>=' <Op Add>
    | <Op Add>

<Op Add>
    ::= <Op Add> '+' <Op Mult>
    | <Op Add> '-' <Op Mult>
    | <Op Mult>

<Op Mult>
    ::= <Op Mult> '*' <Op Unary>
    | <Op Mult> '/' <Op Unary>
    | <Op Mult> '%' <Op Unary>
    | <Op Unary>

<Op Unary>
    ::= not <Op Unary>
    | '!' <Op Unary>
    | '-' <Op Unary>
    | cast '(' <Op Unary> as <QualifiedName> ')'
    | '++' <Op Unary>
    | -- <Op Unary>
    | <Op Pointer> '++'
    | <Op Pointer> --
    | <Op Pointer> is null
    | <Op Pointer> not null
    | <Op Pointer> is not null
    | <Op Pointer>

<Op Pointer>
    ::= <Op Pointer> '.' <Value>
    | <Op Pointer> '->' <Value>
    | <Op Pointer> '[' <Expr> ']'
    | <Op Pointer> '(' <Args> ')'
    | <Value>

<Value>
    ::= IntLiteral
    | StringLiteral
    | DecimalLiteral
    | DateTimeLiteral
    | TimeSpanLiteral
    | type '(' <QualifiedName> ')'
    | new <QualifiedName> '(' <Args> ')'
    | ID
    | var ID
    | static ID
    | '(' <Expr> ')'
    | '[' <Expr List> ']'
    | '{' <Dict List> '}'
    | range '<' <Op Add> ';' <Op Add> '>'
    | range '<' <Op Add> ';' <Op Add> ')'
    | range '(' <Op Add> ';' <Op Add> '>'
    | range '(' <Op Add> ';' <Op Add> ')'
    | property <Expr> ';'
    | property <Expr> get <Expr> ';'
    | property <Expr> get <Expr> set <Expr> ';'
    | <Function>
    | dict
    | list
    | null
    | true
    | false
